ed="T" n="0886b17"/><persName key="A013803">釋從彥</persName>，姓<name>米</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000000514">燕</placeName>人也。始自識環<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1628"/>，尋知跪<lb
ed="T" n="0886b18"/>橘<ptr target="#n3469"/>，顒昂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2304"/>挺質<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2305"/>，豁達為<anchor xml:id="beg0886003"/>襟<anchor xml:id="end0886003"/>。年<anchor xml:id="beg0886004"/>距<anchor xml:id="end0886004"/>十五，父母<lb
ed="T" n="0886b19"/>聽許出家於<placeName key="PL000000003731">并部</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/><placeName key="PL000000003787">慧覺禪院</placeName>也。受戒後，經江<lb
ed="T" n="0886b20"/>鼓枻<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1013"/>，論海化鯤<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2306"/>，流輩畏之，咸知宗奉。乃懷<lb
ed="T" n="0886b21"/>心於祖教，望攻玉於他山<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2307"/>。由是北別氷天，<lb
ed="T" n="0886b22"/>南觀<placeName key="PL000000000153">桂海</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2308"/>，不虞惡瘴，唯慕叢林，欣遇<persName key="A010681">龍牙<lb
ed="T" n="0886b23"/>山<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>為決所疑，蔚成達者。<date from-iso="+0936-02-01" key="j20629582063308" to-iso="+0937-01-16"><name>後唐</name><name>清泰</name>丙<lb
ed="T" n="0886b24"/>申歲</date>還遊<placeName key="PL000000023255">嵩少</placeName>。<placeName key="PL000000023638">洛中</placeName>始安，人情輯睦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2309"/>，<persName key="A013803">彥</persName>營<lb
ed="T" n="0886b25"/>構禪坊，延聚緇侶而供養之。歷<placeName key="PL000000000124">晉</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000057659">漢</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000057658">周</placeName>三<lb
ed="T" n="0886b26"/>朝，皆加恩命，乃曰：「寵辱若驚，<ref type="person" target="#A013803">吾</ref>無驚久矣！<lb
ed="T" n="0886b27"/>然俗諦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1898"/>門中，感世主以綈繡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2310"/>緣飾朽木者<lb
ed="T" n="0886b28"/>哉。」以<date key="j20752452075245" when-iso="+0969-09-22"><name>開寶</name>二年八月三日</date>示疾而終。<date from-iso="+0971-02-04" key="j20757452076098" to-iso="+0972-01-23">四年<lb
ed="T" n="0886b29"/>辛未</date>，改權從久，瘞于層塔焉。</p>
